This paper is about natural language processing and specifically focuses on relation extraction using neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves optimization and training of the neural network, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval and classification, which could make it relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
